ORDER BY [t1].[ParentId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

            WHERE (((DATEPART(year, [n3].[DateCreated]) >= @__fromDate_Year_0) AND (DATEPART(month, [n3].[DateCreated]) >= @__fromDate_Month_1)) AND (DATEPART(day, [n3].[DateCreated]) >= @__fromDate_Day_2)) AND (((DATEPART(year, [n3].[DateCreated]) <= @__toDate_Year_3) AND (DATEPART(month, [n3].[DateCreated]) <= @__toDate_Month_4)) AND (DATEPART(day, [n3].[DateCreated]) <= @__toDate_Day_5))
            ORDER BY [n3].[DateCreated] DESC, [n3].[Id]
            OFFSET @__p_6 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_7 ROWS ONLY
        ) AS [t4] ON [n.BillDetails2].[BillId] = [t4].[Id]
    ) AS [t5] ON [dto.Product.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t5].[Id1]
) AS [t6] ON [dto.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t6].[Id2]

    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
